    "今天已提交过该任务。请先刷新打卡记录，勿重复提交。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Already submitted today. Refresh your check-in records first and do not submit again."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "今天已提交过该任务。请先刷新打卡记录，勿重复提交。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "今日已打卡，不能再次开始运动。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You have already checked in today and cannot start another session."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "今日已打卡，不能再次开始运动。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "今日已打卡，每天只能提交一次。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You have already checked in today. Only one submission per day is allowed."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "今日已打卡，每天只能提交一次。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "仍缺口": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Remaining"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "仍缺口"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "从个人页进入申请中心，选择对应免测类型，填写申请信息并上传证明材料后提交。正式提交和处理结果需要联网并由任课教师审核。": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Open the application center from Profile, choose the exemption type, complete the form, and upload supporting documents. Submission and review results require a network connection and teacher approval."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "从个人页进入申请中心，选择对应免测类型，填写申请信息并上传证明材料后提交。正式提交和处理结果需要联网并由任课教师审核。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "从相册选择": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Choose from Photos"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "从相册选择"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "从相册选择凭证使用系统照片选择器，App 只接收您明确选中的项目；直接拍摄仅在您操作时申请摄像头及录音权限。": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Photo selection uses the system picker, and the app receives only items you explicitly choose. Camera and microphone access is requested only when you capture evidence."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "从相册选择凭证使用系统照片选择器，App 只接收您明确选中的项目；直接拍摄仅在您操作时申请摄像头及录音权限。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
