    "请先确认学号和密码无误。当前 App 尚未接入忘记密码接口；需要重置时，请联系课程教师或系统管理员。": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "First verify your student number and password. Password reset is not yet connected in this app; contact your course teacher or system administrator if a reset is needed."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "请先确认学号和密码无误。当前 App 尚未接入忘记密码接口；需要重置时，请联系课程教师或系统管理员。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "请在 iPhone“设置 → 通知”中允许本 App 发送通知。通知不会包含姓名、具体成绩等个人信息；关键事项也可能通过学校邮箱送达。": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Allow notifications in iPhone Settings → Notifications. Notifications do not include names or specific grades; important items may also be sent to your school email."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "请在 iPhone“设置 → 通知”中允许本 App 发送通知。通知不会包含姓名、具体成绩等个人信息；关键事项也可能通过学校邮箱送达。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "请在 iPhone“设置 → 通知”中允许通知。本版本已支持本地授权、前台展示和点击跳转；服务器推送仍需后端与 APNs 配置。": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Allow notifications in iPhone Settings → Notifications. This version supports permission, foreground presentation, and tap routing; server push still requires backend and APNs configuration."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "请在 iPhone“设置 → 通知”中允许通知。本版本已支持本地授权、前台展示和点击跳转；服务器推送仍需后端与 APNs 配置。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "请在 iPhone“设置 → 隐私与安全性 → 定位服务”中允许本 App 使用定位。定位只在运动开始后尝试获取一次；失败不会阻止计时和提交。": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Allow location access in iPhone Settings → Privacy & Security → Location Services. The app requests one location fix after exercise starts; failure does not block timing or submission."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "请在 iPhone“设置 → 隐私与安全性 → 定位服务”中允许本 App 使用定位。定位只在运动开始后尝试获取一次；失败不会阻止计时和提交。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "请在 iPhone“设置 → 隐私与安全性 → 定位服务”中允许本 App 使用定位。定位失败不会阻止计时和提交，记录会显示为“未获取位置”。": {
