    "运动时长已满 2 小时，计时已自动结束并按 2 小时计入。请补充说明和凭证完成提交。": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Exercise reached 2 hours and ended automatically for 2 credited hours. Add a note and proof to submit."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "运动时长已满 2 小时，计时已自动结束并按 2 小时计入。请补充说明和凭证完成提交。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "运动时长未满 1 小时": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Exercise Is Under 1 Hour"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "运动时长未满 1 小时"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "运动时长未满 1 小时，结束后本次不计入有效打卡时长，也不占用今日打卡次数。已拍摄的照片/视频草稿会保留，今天继续运动后仍可选用。": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Exercise is under 1 hour. Ending earns no credit and does not use today's check-in. Captured drafts are retained for another exercise today."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "运动时长未满 1 小时，结束后本次不计入有效打卡时长，也不占用今日打卡次数。已拍摄的照片/视频草稿会保留，今天继续运动后仍可选用。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "运动有效时长必须达到 1 小时或 2 小时，并至少选择一份运动拍摄凭证。每天只能提交一次。": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Exercise must reach 1 or 2 credited hours and include at least one captured proof. Only one submission is allowed each day."
